tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE game_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_id INT,
    action VARCHAR,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE GameLogs (
	game_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	player_id INT,
	action VARCHAR,
	timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE Players (
	player_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	player_name VARCHAR,
	level INT
)

CREATE TABLE Levels (
	level_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	level_name VARCHAR,
	score INT
)

CREATE TABLE Items (
	item_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	item_name VARCHAR,
	item_type VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE PlayerInventory (
	player_id INT,
	item_id INT,
	quantity INT
)
